---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="NEXIS // TERMINAL">
  <main class="content-wrapper">
    <header class="hero">
      <h1 class="gradient-text">SYSTEM_OVERRIDE: NEXIS</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">[ ACCESS_LEVEL: ROOT ]</p>
    </header>

    <section class="prose">
      <h2 class="section-title">> _INITIALIZING_LOREM_IPSUM...</h2>
      
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. 
        <strong>Nullam in dui mauris.</strong> Vivamus hendrerit arcu sed erat 
        molestie vehicula. Sed auctor neque eu tellus rhoncus ut eleifend 
        nibh porttitor. Ut in nulla enim.
      </p>

      <ul class="terminal-list">
        <li>[CYPHERPUNKS] Proin quis tortor orci.</li>
        <li>[WRITE] Etiam at risus et justo dignissim.</li>
        <li>[CODE] Donec vel mauris quis erat.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Curabitur sem ante, interdum vel suscipit sed, egestas ut ipsum. 
        Nam imperdiet elit eu neque iaculis iaculis. 
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 70ch;
    color: var(--text-main);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .section-title {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-muted);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .terminal-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.05);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .terminal-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
</style>